1
00:00:01,667 --> 00:00:06,591
<i>During final exams, Haruhi, who suffered
about of melancholy during the Star Festival,</i>

2
00:00:06,616 --> 00:00:10,901
<i>had recovered from the aforementioned melancholy
enough to go back to doing whatever she wanted to do.</i>

3
00:00:11,320 --> 00:00:14,906
<i>However, as an adverse reaction
to her emotional improvement,</i>

4
00:00:15,004 --> 00:00:18,212
<i>the blue-colored baton of
depression had been handed off to me.</i>

5
00:00:19,201 --> 00:00:23,414
<i>Haruhi always seemed to have time left over
during an exam, and today was no exception.</i>

6
00:00:23,623 --> 00:00:27,932
<i>About 30 minutes before pencils down,
she was sound asleep in the desk behind me.</i>

7
00:00:28,510 --> 00:00:30,529
<i>Annoying. Oh, it's annoying.</i>

8
00:00:30,696 --> 00:00:31,895
<i>It's so annoying.</i>

9
00:02:02,833 --> 00:02:06,423
<i>According to Haruhi, there is no such
thing as a break for the SOS Brigade.</i>

10
00:02:06,709 --> 00:02:09,856
<i>Even during exam time, when all
the other clubs went on hiatus,</i>

11
00:02:09,922 --> 00:02:14,781
<i>this mysterious brigade, which wasn't really
even a club, was open every day without a holiday.</i>

12
00:02:14,978 --> 00:02:16,502
<i>Kinda like a convenient store...</i>

13
00:02:17,312 --> 00:02:19,319
Hey, come take a look at this.

14
00:02:25,195 --> 00:02:25,819
