31
00:03:12,968 --> 00:03:14,808
It's all because you got in my way.

32
00:03:14,881 --> 00:03:18,710
We'd've had a ton of hits if you'd
let me post these erotic pics of Mikuru.

33
00:03:18,927 --> 00:03:24,014
So I got to thinkin', I should paste a cool
logo or symbol for the SOS Brigade on the homepage.

34
00:03:24,083 --> 00:03:27,359
<i>Just get this stupid excuse
for a website off the net already.</i>

35
00:03:27,548 --> 00:03:30,041
<i>The access counter hasn't even reached three digits yet,</i>

36
00:03:30,132 --> 00:03:33,453
<i>and 90% of those hits have been
you checking the site for hits.</i>

37
00:03:34,103 --> 00:03:35,844
Write a blog on there or something.

38
00:03:36,094 --> 00:03:38,909
Isn't it your job to keep a
record of the brigade's activities?

39
00:03:38,956 --> 00:03:40,369
Ugh, too much of a hassle.

40
00:03:40,498 --> 00:03:42,021
<i>Well, it's a hassle for me, too.</i>

41
00:03:43,641 --> 00:03:48,416
Okay, Kyon, your job for today is to make
this logo show up on the homepage of the website.

42
00:03:48,511 --> 00:03:50,027
Why don't you do it yourself?

43
00:03:50,139 --> 00:03:54,061
I'm the brigade leader! It's the job
of the brigade leader to give the orders!

44
00:03:54,198 --> 00:03:58,207
Besides, if I did everything, there'd be
nothing left for you guys to do, isn't that right?

45
00:03:58,308 --> 00:04:02,895
I'm always spelling this stuff out for you, why don't
you use your head? How do you expect to improve yourself,

46
00:04:02,920 --> 00:04:04,212
if you only do what you're told?

47
00:04:04,237 --> 00:04:06,054
There you go, talking in circles again.

48
00:04:06,079 --> 00:04:08,505
Are you telling me to do it or not to do it? Which is it?

49
00:04:08,617 --> 00:04:10,409
Enough! Get on it!

50
00:04:12,596 --> 00:04:17,583
<i>Reluctantly, I shrunk the master painter
Haruhi's tapeworm into an appropriate size.</i>

51
00:04:17,814 --> 00:04:21,750
<i>Then, I pasted it, still reluctantly,
into the file, and uploaded it.</i>

52
00:04:22,705 --> 00:04:27,022
<i>Starting tomorrow and lasting until summer
vacation, we get to have our exam break.</i>

53
00:04:27,422 --> 00:04:30,070
<i>It's also the time when my
teacher's mark my answers wrong.</i>

54
00:04:31,155 --> 00:04:32,455
<i>Damn, that's annoying.</i>

55
00:04:32,927 --> 00:04:35,550
<i>Guess I'll go and ogle Miss Asahina for some comfort.</i>

56
00:04:36,396 --> 00:04:41,305
<i>I knocked on the door, fully expecting Miss
Asahina's voice to call out a wispy "Yes" in reply.</i>

57
00:04:41,330 --> 00:04:42,191
Come in.

58
00:04:44,683 --> 00:04:45,847
You're the only one here?

59
00:04:46,322 --> 00:04:47,638
